# Check the status of a guarantee balance request

Use the GET endpoint [Check the status of a balance request](/api-documentation/docs/api/service/common-transit-convention-guarantee-balance/1.0/oas/page#tag/ctc-guarantee-balance-api/operation/CheckthestatusofaBalanceRequest) to check the status of a balance request for which a response could not be provided immediately.  You can use the `balanceId` returned by the 202 (Accepted) response to call this resource.

JSON schema files and example requests are available in the [CTC Guarantee Balance API phase 4 testing guide](/guides/ctc-guarantee-balance-testing-guide/).
